==重啟==
2015年，新的《飛俠哥頓》電影計畫被提出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/flash-gordon-movie-works-at-698291|title='Flash Gordon' Movie in the Works at Fox (Exclusive)|last=Kit|first=Borys|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2014-04-22|accessdate=2014-04-24|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324133754/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/flash-gordon-movie-works-at-698291|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[二十世紀福斯|二十世紀福斯]]聘請了JD·佩恩和派翠克·麥凱撰寫劇本，而[[馬修·范恩|馬修·范恩]]則在談判擔任導演一職<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/matthew-vaughn-talks-direct-flash-788921|title=Matthew Vaughn in Talks to Direct 'Flash Gordon' (Exclusive)|publisher=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2015-04-15|accessdate=2015-04-15|archive-date=2016-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160819115048/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/matthew-vaughn-talks-direct-flash-788921|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年1月15日，{{le|馬克·普羅塞維奇|Mark Protosevich}}被聘來為電影改寫劇本<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hitfix.com/motion-captured/mark-protosevich-hired-to-rewrite-matthew-vaughns-flash-gordon-for-fox |title=Mark Protosevich Hired To Rewrite Matthew Vaughn's 'Flash Gordon' For Fox |publisher=Hitfix |last=McWeeny |first=Drew |date=January 2016 |access-date=2016-11-17 |archive-date=2016-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610132101/http://www.hitfix.com/motion-captured/mark-protosevich-hired-to-rewrite-matthew-vaughns-flash-gordon-for-fox |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2018年10月底，朱利斯·艾弗里被選來擔任導演<ref name="Variety(2018-10-30)">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/overlord-director-flash-gordon-movie-1203015289/|title='Overlord' Filmmaker Julius Avery to Direct 'Flash Gordon' Movie|last=McNary|first=Dave|work=Variety|date=2018-10-30|accessdate=2018-11-01|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125231237/https://variety.com/2018/film/news/overlord-director-flash-gordon-movie-1203015289/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2019年3月20日，随着迪士尼收购福斯，原本的真人版计划被取消。2019年6月24日，迪士尼宣布开发该作的动画版电影，制作商改为福斯与迪士尼联合制作。

